Module PIXL.POS
Package teampixl.com.pixlpos.database.api

Class UsersAPI

java.lang.Object
teampixl.com.pixlpos.database.api.UsersAPI
public class UsersAPI extends Object
The UsersAPI class is a singleton class that manages user operations. It handles validation, retrieval, creation, updating, and deletion of users. Internal operations are optimized for asynchronous execution where applicable.
